# Candidate doctrine-edit skill copies for eval A/B (control=installed plugin,
# treatment=experiments/<name>/skills). Never committed as files - only the
# RESULT (maps, verdicts) and the diff-vs-installed get banked to data/. Keeps
# real doctrine text out of the cockpit's history. See AGENTS.md "Eval tier".
experiments/

# Local secrets for eval providers (SAIA key etc.) — never committed. eval-leg.sh
# reads the key non-printing and injects it only into the throwaway eval $HOME.
.env.local
*.saia.env
.saia.env

# Batch scratch (fresh sim trees per model) — never committed.
.eval-scratch/
